    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Why is it limited to numeric values? The use case looks like it could use any kind of refinement (strings).\n\nWe could probably build a `facetSelector` as well but not sure we want to mix it in a single widget: I think it's easier to understand not mixing the `operator` VS `disjunctive` VS .... Also the underlying code would be pretty different because of that `operator`. WDYT?\n",
